project-basis: What makes my project unique is the technologies used. One of the biggest advantage my project has is the ability to recognize when a user is stopped for a period of time and when that user is moving. This allows for accurate readings on congestion.
project-purpose: My project notifies residents when the Hsuehshan Tunnel is backed up. It sends notifications to residents when there is a backup at the tunnel.
project-inspiration: I lived in a town where there was always traffic and I always wished there was a way for me to know which route is backed up
project-subtitle: Notify residents when Hsuehshan Tunnel gets backed up
